{"type":null,"faqId":7539,"title":"省电小窍门","answer":"1、 不使用手机时，按电源键关闭屏幕；<br />\n2、 缩短屏幕待机时间：进入主菜单-&gt;设置-&gt;声音和显示-&gt;屏幕待机；<br />\n3、 降低屏幕亮度：进入主菜单-&gt;设置-&gt;声音和显示-&gt;亮度；<br />\n4、 关闭蓝牙和wifi：进入主菜单-&gt;设置-&gt;无线和网络-&gt;取消勾选无线局域网/蓝牙；<br />\n5、 关闭后台数据同步：进入主菜单-&gt;设置-&gt;帐户与同步-&gt;取消勾选后台数据/自动同步；<br />\n6、 关闭数据业务：进入主菜单-&gt;设置-&gt;无线和网络-&gt;移动网络-&gt;取消勾选数据业务；<br />\n7、 关闭GPS：进入主菜单-&gt;设置-&gt;地点和安全-&gt;适用GPS 卫星；<br />\n8、 使用2G sim 卡时，勾选“设置-&gt;无线和网络-&gt;移动网络-&gt;仅适用2G 网络”。","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7679","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1321432996000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":517,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":36,"times":8,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":4.5,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}